text: Zegartowice is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Papowo Biskupie, within Chełmno County, Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship, in north- central Poland. ==Gallery== File:Droga E75 Chełmno-Toruń.JPG File:Przystanek w Zegartowicach.JPG Category:Villages in Kuyavian-Pomeranian Voivodeship
